    "id": "D2-Q008",
    "question_text": "A company's retention schedule specifies deletion of customer interaction logs after 2 years. Legal counsel has just issued a litigation hold covering all customer interactions from the past 5 years. Which action is MOST appropriate?",
    "section": "Asset Security",
    "topic": "",
    "difficulty_label": "Medium",
