    "question_text": "A research team wants to use a 'fully anonymized' customer dataset for a public research publication. The dataset contains aggregated purchase history with direct identifiers removed but retains ZIP code, birth date, and gender. What is the CORRECT assessment of this dataset under GDPR?",
