      {
        "index": 1,
        "text": "Delete every backup that contains the record, regardless of other records in those backups"
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "text": "Document the erasure request, delete the primary record, mark the subject's identifiers in the backup index so that backups cannot be restored for that subject (and if restored, the erasure is re-applied), align backup retention to the erasure schedule, and respond to the data subject that the primary record is erased and backups will be rotated out within the standard retention window"
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "text": "Inform the data subject that erasure is not possible in a cloud environment"
      }
