    "id": "D2-Q040",
    "question_text": "A SaaS company hosts data for customers in multiple regulated industries (healthcare, finance, education). A new customer requests that their data be isolated from other customers' data at every layer — compute, storage, and network — rather than in a shared multi-tenant environment. Which architectural pattern BEST supports this requirement?",
    "section": "Asset Security",
