    "id": "D2-Q041",
    "question_text": "A company's 'shred-and-go' program manually destroys paper documents but has no corresponding process for end-of-life servers and storage media. An audit finds decommissioned servers in a storage room, some containing Confidential data. Which root cause is MOST likely?",
    "section": "Asset Security",
