    "id": "D3-Q034",
    "question_text": "A CISSP is evaluating a legacy application that stores session tokens as unsalted MD5 hashes of usernames in a database. Which combination of issues is MOST CRITICAL to address?",
    "section": "Security Architecture & Engineering",
    "topic": "",
    "difficulty_label": "Medium",
