        "index": 1,
        "text": "FDE protects data at rest on powered-off devices; it does not protect a running device from malware, a logged-in device from theft with the screen unlocked, or data already copied off the device. The policy should assume FDE is a baseline control and combine it with endpoint detection, strong authentication, remote wipe capability, DLP, and awareness training"
