    "id": "D3-Q040",
    "question_text": "A CISSP is reviewing the physical security design of a data center and notices that the entrance uses a single-factor card reader. The facility contains Restricted-class customer data. Which improvement is MOST EFFECTIVE given that cost and operational impact are both concerns?",
