    "id": "D4-Q034",
    "question_text": "A CISSP is evaluating a design for a new multi-region deployment. The design uses public DNS load balancing (GeoDNS) to route users to the nearest region. Which consideration is MOST IMPORTANT from a security standpoint?",
    "section": "Communication & Network Security",
