    "id": "D5-Q032",
    "question_text": "A CISSP is asked to evaluate the claim that 'MFA solves the credential theft problem'. Which response is MOST ACCURATE?",
    "section": "Identity & Access Management (IAM)",
    "topic": "",
    "difficulty_label": "Medium",
