        "text": "Prioritize based on actual exploitability (EPSS, known-exploited lists like CISA KEV), business context (public-facing vs internal, data sensitivity, compensating controls), and threat intelligence (active campaigns targeting the vulnerability), not just the CVSS base score; CVSS is a starting point, not the full picture"
