        "text": "Implement cloud-native policy-as-code (AWS Config Rules, Azure Policy, GCP Organization Policies, or multi-cloud via Cloud Custodian, Prisma Cloud, Wiz, etc.), map policies to relevant control frameworks (SOC 2, ISO 27001, PCI-DSS, NIST), detect violations in real time, automate remediation for well-understood patterns, escalate exceptions to governance for decision, and generate evidence reports for audit automation"
