    "id": "D6-Q029",
    "question_text": "A CISSP is evaluating a new attack simulation platform that runs automated tests against the organization's defenses based on MITRE ATT&CK techniques. Which is the MOST VALUABLE benefit of such a platform?",
    "section": "Security Assessment & Testing",
