        "index": 1,
        "text": "Add immutable or air-gapped backups that cannot be destroyed by ransomware reaching the primary network, test restore procedures regularly, and consider replicated cloud backups with verified integrity; the 3-2-1-1-0 rule reflects modern requirements beyond the classic 3-2-1"
