        "text": "Assess vulnerability exploitability (active exploitation in the wild, public exploit available, compensating controls in place), severity, and business impact of the outage; if critical exploitation risk justifies the outage, proceed with emergency change management and scheduled downtime communication; if compensating controls can bridge to a planned window, use them"
