        "index": 1,
        "text": "Authentication logs (IdP, identity events), cloud control plane logs (CloudTrail, Activity Log, Audit Log), network flow logs, application access logs, and security tool logs (EDR, DLP, IDS/IPS), with sufficient retention to cover typical dwell times; avoid collecting only what is easy and missing what matters for investigation"
