        "text": "Blameless post-mortem that focuses on root cause analysis, identifies systemic issues rather than individual mistakes, captures contributing factors, produces specific remediation actions with owners and deadlines, and follows up on remediation completion as a closed loop; blame-focused reviews drive silence and prevent learning"
